definition: on top/upon/above/upper/previous/first (of multiple parts)/to climb/to get onto/to go up/to attend (class or university)

sentences.english: Something seems to be pressing on the upper right-hand side of my stomach.
sentences.chinese: 好像有什麼東西壓在我胃部右上方。

sentences.english: My mouse cursor is over here on the top right, now, I touch the cat.
sentences.chinese: 我們鼠標移到右上方時，我們摸了下貓。

sentences.english: Visible on the upper right are the crescent Moon and the bright planet Venus.
sentences.chinese: 右上角可見弦月與一旁明亮的金星。

sentences.english: When going through the door, look up and right and you'll see an alcove.
sentences.chinese: 進門之後向右上方看，你將找到一個壁龕。

sentences.english: This will add the image on the top-right corner of the page.
sentences.chinese: 這將會在頁面的右上角添加圖形。

sentences.english: The TEWS (Tactical Electronic Warfare System) is positioned in the upper right corner of the instrument panel .
sentences.chinese: 電子戰術威脅顯示器位於儀表板的右上方。

sentences.english: There is focal atrophy of tubules seen here to the upper right.
sentences.chinese: 右上方可見生精小管的竈狀萎縮。

sentences.english: Shorrock took the penalty kick making the ball swerve into the top right-hand corner of the net.
sentences.chinese: 罰點球時，肖羅克一個弧線球將球踢進右上角。

sentences.english: The upper-right pane shows the values of variables.
sentences.chinese: 右上方的窗格顯示變量的值。

sentences.english: Classes containing connection and interaction information appear in the upper-right pane.
sentences.chinese: 包含連接和交互信息的類在右上方窗格中出現。

sentences.english: The guest of honour is seated on the right side of the hostess.
When the cursor is hovering over a launcher, a pin icon will appear in the top right-hand corner.
sentences.chinese: 當光標指向啓動項時，右上角會出現一個大頭針圖標。

sentences.english: The picture at upper right shows a relatively calm galaxy called NGC 4145.
sentences.chinese: 右上角的這張照片是相對處於平靜期的4145星系。

sentences.english: Please write your address on the top righthand corner when you write a letter.
sentences.chinese: 寫信時，請把地址寫在右上角。

sentences.english: Remember to mark the position you apply on the left-down side of the envelop and cover of resume.
sentences.chinese: 請在信封左下角和簡歷首頁右上角註明應聘職位名稱。

sentences.english: For your application, you want it to show in the top right corner.
sentences.chinese: 對於您的應用程序，您希望它顯示在屏幕的右上角。

definition: left/the left side/to the left of
gap in coverage/gap in protection or defenses/neglected or overlooked area/dead end
